Qwen3.5 punches above its weight class

<break time="1s" />
Alibaba released the Qwen3.5 family of open weights vision-language models this week, including impressive larger models as well as a smaller one that outperforms an OpenAI open weights model ten times its size. The Qwen3.5 family uses a mixture of experts architecture and is available in sizes ranging from less than one billion parameters upward. The release continues a pattern from Chinese labs of releasing highly capable open weights models that perform well above what their parameter counts would suggest.

